<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I read this play for class during the first semester of my senior year of high school. I was 17, and it helped inspire my love of reading, but I don&apos;t<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I read this play for class during the first semester of my senior year of high school. I was 17, and it helped inspire my love of reading, but I don't recommend going much younger than that (16 is the youngest I would go for this one, and only if they're somewhat mature for their age). <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
