        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1559329036" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11249481852723001653">To start with, this is funny. Really, really funny. Laugh out loud funny at parts.<br/><br/>It’s also a bit dark. Okay, more than a bit. Really dark. Pitch black dark. But funny. <br/><br/>Hopefully this play will make you a bit uncomfortable. It’s not pleasant, and it’s not an easy read. Not because it’s particularly convoluted, but due to the whole “pitch black” thing. You could describe it as “shocking” and not wander far from the truth. Hopefully this play will make you a bit uncomfortable, because I’m not quit</span>
  <span id="freeText11249481852723001653" style="display:none">To start with, this is funny. Really, really funny. Laugh out loud funny at parts.<br /><br />It’s also a bit dark. Okay, more than a bit. Really dark. Pitch black dark. But funny. <br /><br />Hopefully this play will make you a bit uncomfortable. It’s not pleasant, and it’s not an easy read. Not because it’s particularly convoluted, but due to the whole “pitch black” thing. You could describe it as “shocking” and not wander far from the truth. Hopefully this play will make you a bit uncomfortable, because I’m not quite sure what to make of you if it doesn’t.<br /><br />But, remember, it’s funny. Really. Really. Funny.<br /></span>
