<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer11954849583759625201">While still in his twenties, the Anglo-Irish playwright Martin McDonagh filled houses in New York and London, was showered with the theatre world&apos;s most prestigious accolades, and electrified audiences with his cunningly crafted and outrageous tragicomedies.</span>
  <span id="freeText11954849583759625201" style="display:none">While still in his twenties, the Anglo-Irish playwright Martin McDonagh filled houses in New York and London, was showered with the theatre world's most prestigious accolades, and electrified audiences with his cunningly crafted and outrageous tragicomedies.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11954849583759625201" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

